fields.title: Dockside apartments
fields.content:
Introducing Dockside Apartments

Ideally situated within a popular L3 postcode in Liverpool and within the massive £5 billion Liverpool Water Scheme. This development is a stunning collection of elegant apartments nestled in a prime waterfront setting with easy access to a wide range of local amenities and Liverpool’s centre. Each apartment is designed for comfort and to offer the ideal place to relax and a lifestyle that is second to none.

AREA

This stunning development is located in an area set to receive a £5Bn regeneration, through the Liverpool Waters scheme. As the largest single development opportunity in the city, Liverpool Waters is a seamless extension of both Liverpool’s Commercial Business District and its iconic world heritage waterfront. Set to extend to over 2km along the banks of the River Mersey, this £5Bn scheme has outline planning permission for 20 million sq ft of mixed-use development floor space across 60 hectares. The transportation links surrounding this development are plentiful also, with Liverpool Lime Street Station falling a short walking distance away also.

PROPERTY HIGHLIGHT’S

  • Situated on Liverpool’s Historic Waterloo Dock
  • Breath-Taking Views of Leeds and Liverpool Canal and River Mersey
  • Award-Winning Developer
  • Walking Distance From The Main Liverpool Universities, Including Liverpool John Moores University & Liverpool Lime Street Station
  • 24/7 Concierge & Security Services
  • Completion 2024 & Zero Ground Rent

 

LIVERPOOL INSIGHTS

When compared to other major UK cities, it is evident that property prices in Liverpool are considerably lower. As of June 2022, the average property price in Liverpool was £186k, compared to London’s average of £523k. The difference is staggering however, Liverpool is set to see a large trajectory over the next decade and so investing and purchasing now before prices increase further is essential. Read more.

Contact us today and receive the Development Brochure alongside any further information.

It's a new luxury development that offers a fantastic investment opportunity for capital growth, the perfect opportunity for first-time buyers or investors.
Our new development features four iconic towers, each with unique façades with a stunning architectural design. Each tower is set within a modern landscaped public realm, which features cafe spaces, restaurants, retail and office space alongside the residential offer. With heights ranging between 14 and 35 floors, the towers provide sweeping views of MediaCityUK, Salford Quays and central Manchester.

X1 are a massive multibillion-pound developer with extensive experience in developing high-quality housing and working closely with Peel Ports.
Rental Guarantee to offset any void periods during the first 2-3 years.
Hand-free investment

X1 Michigan Towers is a stunning, luxury residential apartment complex conveniently located at the heart of the UK’s television, radio and digital production hub. The properties are being built by an award-winning developer, with the finished project expected to generate exceptionally high demand from tenants in the local area. In the heart of MediaCityUK, Michigan Towers is conveniently located for young professionals working in the area, including quick and simple connections to the city centre via Manchester’s tram system, situated in the heart of MediaCityUK in the iconic Salford Quays, home to Coronation Street as well as the likes of the BBC, ITV, Ericsson and Kellogg’s. There is an excellent selection of shops, bars and restaurants within walking distance, as well as cultural highlights such as the Lowry Theatre and the Imperial War Museum North.
Next to MediaCityUK, home to the BBC, ITV, Kellogg's, Bupa, University of Salford and over 250 creative media businesses.
8 Mins into central Manchester
20 min walk to Old Trafford Football Ground
Part of the Peel Group’s multi-billion-pound regeneration scheme.

fields.title: Broadway residence
fields.content:
We are excited to introduce you to the Broadway Residence on Well Street in the heart of Bradford City Centre. It is ideally suited for tenants wanting to live in the city centre and looking for excellent quality apartments. The development offers the best high-end accommodation in the area and a fantastic location.
Broadway Residence is a refurbishment development scheme providing residents with an essential, central living environment.
Broadway Residence is a centrally located residential development consisting of a collection of only 59 studio, 1-bedroom, and 2-bedroom apartments.

The development will retain its unique contemporary style, and apartments will be finished to a high standard with a minimalist design, which is also ideal for the short-term rental market.

The apartments feature fitted kitchen units with a high gloss finish, impeccable en-suite bath & shower rooms, and premium quality flooring.
There are satellite TV and telephone outlets in the living room and bedrooms. There is a secure intercom entry system for all apartments.

This is a great investment opportunity for investors looking for guaranteed rental income, as the developer has partnered with Dream Apartments to offer a 10-year rental guarantee on all units.
Starting discounted launch prices are below market value price.
Contact us today to get the development brochure.

AREA

Bradford benefits from excellent transport links by road and rail. The future Northern Powerhouse railway station will connect to Leeds in just 7 minutes and Manchester in 20 minutes, making Bradford a desirable commuter location.
Broadway Residence is ideally located for those seeking accommodation in the city centre. It is on the doorstep of the new £260 million Broadway shopping centre, featuring some of the city's best restaurants and bars.

Broadway Residence benefits from excellent connectivity, just 6 minute walk from Bradford Interchange Station, with a short journey to Leeds.

PROPERTY HIGHLIGHTS

  • Prime Central Location

  • One & Two bed Contemporary Apartments

  • Price from £70,000

  • Estimated Completion Q2 2023

  • 6% Net Rental Guarantee for 10-year 

  • AirB&B Friendly

  • Proven Developer with Over 20 Years of Experience

  • On the Doorstep of Broadway Shopping Centre

  • Easy Access to 70+ Restaurants, Cafes, and Shops

  • Prime City Centre Living

  • 10-year Rental Guarantee on All Units

  • Secured Bicycle Storage

  • Completion Q2 2023

  • Ideally situated in the BD1 postcode.

  • This development will be on the doorstep of the brand new £260 million Broadway shopping centre, providing sought-after city centre living. 

 

BIRMINGHAM’S INSIGHTS

  • The Bradford property market is relatively cheap, landing at £164,210. Strikingly low, especially compared to the UK's £281,161 Average

  • Bradford is exceptionally well-connected to Leeds, Harrogate, York and Manchester. All an hour or less from the city centre
    Those selecting Bradford's buy-to-let market will be exposed to impressive yields of 5% from the average rent of £684.20 PCM. The rental yield here is 1.37% above the calculated UK national average.

  • One of the top BTL hotspots in the UK right now, Bradford's economic and in-demand real estate market presents investors with a fantastic chance to purchase low-cost property before the region experiences the 28% increase predicted by industry experts Savills. Professional residents seeking city-centre urban living have a significant demand for rentals due to the economy's and population's rapid growth. One of the UK's youngest populations adds to this demand among students and recent graduates.

  • The city appears to be on track for continued growth with the Northern Powerhouse's ongoing development, which will be greatly aided by the potential introduction of the Northern Powerhouse Rail project, which is expected to improve transportation connections to the rest of the UK and generate an estimated £15 billion.

fields.title: X1 manchester waters
fields.adddress: Pomona strand, old trafford, stretford, manchester
fields.content:
X1 Manchester Waters is a residential development located close to the centre of the UK’s ‘second city’ of Manchester.

The development is set to be the perfect retreat, overlooking the tranquil waterfront whilst being near Manchester’s vibrant city centre, offering tenants the best of both worlds. This outstandingand exceptional waterside  development is comprised of five phases and a total of more than 500 apartments, which will be furnished to the highest standard.

Ranging from spacious studios to high-end three beds, most apartments will benefit from the spectacular view of the waterfront.
a variaty of contemporary apartments comprising an open-plan kitchen living room and full size bathroom.
Towers A and B are fully complete and operational; Block D is the most recent addition to the market and is the tower where you can secure a 6% net assured return for 2 years.

AREA

Pomona Island is the gateway to the city of Manchester. This development is sure to be extremely popular with residents looking for high-quality rental accommodation in a location close to the city centre but remains a tranquil retreat.
With two Metrolink stops within a 5-minute walk, residents can easily reach Manchester's city centre and enjoy everything the Capital of the North has to offer. Additionally, residents are just a short journey away from major tourist destinations like Manchester United's Old Trafford, Intu Trafford Centre and MediaCityUK.

X1 Manchester Waters is an excellent long-term investment, as Manchester is one of the UK's strongest regional economies and is forecast to grow faster than any other Northern city.
